  displayName: Furosemide
  dialogueOne: It looks like you've been [prescribed Furosemide]?
  dialogueTwo: The water pill? Yes...
  dialogueThree: Good to know. It's a diuretic and we may have to check your glucose
    levels/eletrolytes if that's the case.
  nextSO: 
  symptomSO: Taking Furosemide to mitigate water retention, check for glucose/electrolyte
    levels
